<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.6">
<l>muṭiyoṉṟi mūvula kaṅkaḷu māṇṭu</l>
<l>ṉaṭiyēṟ karuḷeṉ ṟavaṉpiṉ toṭarnta</l>
<l>paṭiyil kuṇattup paratanampik kaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṭinilai yīntāṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rebd="indent">vayōttiyar kōmāṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the one who gave [his] sandals</l>
<l rend="indent">to prince Bharata,</l>
<l rend="indent">with incomparable qualities,</l>
<l rend="indent">who followed behind [Him] that day saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Accept the crown, rule the three worlds,</l>
<l rend="indent">grace me - your servant!”</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the king of Ayodhyā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
